[This FMDV-O epizootic started in China on 18 Nov 2014 and is considered by the Chinese to be continuing since.

Links to the 4 previous reports, and an interactive map presenting the locations of the 4 accumulated outbreaks, are available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?fupser=&dothis=&reportid=16587.

Outbreak summary:
Total outbreaks = 4 (Submitted)
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Swine / 608 / 220 / 145 / 463 / 0
Cattle / 50 / 7 / 2 / 48 / 0

China applies stamping out policy for the control of FMD. - Mod.AS

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4653143,343.]
